   Corrections &amp; Amplifications
                                                                                                       

   ESOP FINANCE TRUST's 9.35% Eurobonds due June 27, 1995,
are not guaranteed by Exxon Corp. In Friday's list of New
Securities Issues, it was incorrectly stated that the bonds
are guaranteed by Exxon.
   (WSJ June 4, 1990)
